9","name":"Baby Snake-by-the-lake","type":"Run","date":"2023-01-25T22:22:23","description":"Just stretching the legs after yesterday\u2019s big effort","distance_mi":1.36,"moving_time_s":725,"elevation_m":14.0,"avg_hr":null,"max_hr":null,"avg_cadence":84,"calories":183,"with_pet":null,"with_kid":null},{"id":"8457584756","name":"The Control of Nature","type":"Run","date":"2023-01-26T19:05:11","description":"In the \u201880s John McPhee wrote a book with this ironic title which featured a long essay about these mountains \u2014 the San Gabriels that rim the LA basin to the north. There is an ongoing battle between the San Andreas fault which is trying to raise the mountains and the storms like the ones we have had recently which are trying to wash the mountains down. The San Andreas is winning and the mountains are still ascending. Seeing one of the \u201cdebris dams\u201d on this hike reminded me of the book, and the effort required to keep this trail passable on the ever-steepening slopes was a sober reminder of how puny our efforts sometimes are.","distance_mi":12.08,"moving_time_s":11175,"elevation_m":816.0,"avg_hr":null,"max_hr":null,"avg_cadence":63,"calories":1288,"with_pet":null,"with_kid":null},{"id":"8461243190","name":"Quick hike in the hills with Chris","type":"Hike","date":"2023-01-27T17:09:50","description":null,"distance_mi":1.75,"moving_time_s":2600,"elevation_m":125.0,"avg_hr":null,"max_hr":null,"avg_cadence":58,"calories":171,"with_pet":null,"with_kid":null},{"id":"8467502446","name":"Hollywood Res. with Chris and Steve","type":"Run","date":"2023-01-28T19:00:55","description":null,"distance_mi":3.14,"moving_time_s":1627,"elevation_m":9.0,"avg_hr":null,"max_hr":null,"avg_cadence":84,"calories":416,"with_pet":null,"with_kid":null},{"id":"8473083201","name":"Checking out the neighborhood","type":"Run","date":"2023-01-29T17:30:59","description":null,"distance_mi":2.33,"moving_time_s":1237,"elevation_m":7.0,"avg_hr":null,"max_hr":null,"avg_cadence":85,"ca